{
    "name": "Apothecary",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Apothecary",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 220
                }
            ],
            "html": "Surrounded by bottles and bins of crushed herbs, curative minerals, and potent extracts, the apothecary skillfully combines materials into unguents and medicines. For encounters involving making medicine or alchemical contests, the apothecary is a 3rd-level challenge.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 13"
        },
        {
            "name": "Healers",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Ailments",
                    "type": "section",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                                "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                            },
                            "page": 220
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "advice_and_rules",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Advice and Rules",
                        "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                    },
                    "html": "Common diseases are located <a href=\"Diseases.aspx\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\">here</a>. These can be treated by most healers, though they may have longer-term physiological impacts. For unusual conditions, like <a aonid=\"218\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">ghoul fever</a> or <a aonid=\"304\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">mummy rot</a>, you might impose penalties on a normal healer attempting to remedy them."
                },
                {
                    "name": "Medical Service Prices",
                    "type": "section",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                                "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                            },
                            "page": 220
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "advice_and_rules",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Advice and Rules",
                        "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                    },
                    "html": "The <a aonid=\"909\" game-obj=\"NPCs\">physician</a> and <a aonid=\"910\" game-obj=\"NPCs\">surgeon</a> are masters of <a aonid=\"9\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Medicine</a>; the <a aonid=\"908\" game-obj=\"NPCs\">apothecary</a> and <a aonid=\"911\" game-obj=\"NPCs\">plague doctor</a> are experts. Plague doctors charge five times this rate, and surgeons 10 times. <br/><br/><b>Identify Affliction</b>: 1 sp. <br/><a aonid=\"57\" game-obj=\"Actions\"><b>Treat Wounds</b></a>: 2 sp. <br/><a aonid=\"55\" game-obj=\"Actions\"><b>Treat Disease</b></a>: 1 gp. <br/><b><a aonid=\"54\" game-obj=\"Actions\">First Aid</a> or <a aonid=\"56\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Treating a Poison</a></b>: 1 sp."
                }
            ],
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 220",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 220
                }
            ],
            "html": "The world is a dangerous place. Thankfully, there are those who devote their lives to easing the pain and suffering of others."
        }
    ],
